{
  "stem": "26728.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We could smell this camp-- this is Buchenwald now-- from about a mile away, from about where we landed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You could smell something very disagreeable.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I asked the sergeant when I-- the guy that I connected up with was a Signal Corps guy who had been in the camp and taken pictures and was running around just trying to help people like me see what was going on.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we're driving toward the entrance to the camp, and all of these camps from a distance looked the same.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They all had the same kind of gates.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They all had the same towers on concrete or brick towers on each side.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They all had enclosures of barbed wire and electric fences.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They all had moats of one kind or another.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some of them were out in the open.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some of them were in semi-wooded areas.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were usually-- inside of each of the main camps were a section that was all barbed wired so you couldn't get in or out at all with special prisoners in there, which were left-- they were starving them to death.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If you committed some kind of-- there'd be 40, 50 men in there, no clothes no water, no food, no nothing, no shelter, no blankets, and they left them there till they died.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then they'd have to take the barbed wire out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there probably would be-- half of them would be dead.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, I saw this at Buchenwald and also at Dachau.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sorry?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, inside the enclosure, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, there were some-- they had already started to dismantle.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When this sergeant showed this to me, he explained to me what this was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, he'd been there for at least a day, so he knew pretty much where everything was.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
